{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "7fa1bc82-59e5-4f48-a0af-6f9661fbe2b1",
		"name": "MVC Helpdesk – API REST v1",
		"description": "API REST completa del sistema MVC Helpdesk.\n\n**Base URL:** `http://localhost/MVC/api/v1`\n\n**Autenticación:** Bearer token.\n1. Llama a POST /auth/login con tus credenciales.\n2. Copia el `access_token` de la respuesta a la variable de colección `token`.\n3. Todas las demás peticiones envían automáticamente `Authorization: Bearer {{token}}`.\n\n**Códigos de estado:**\n- 200 OK, 201 Created\n- 400 Bad Request, 401 Unauthorized, 403 Forbidden\n- 404 Not Found, 405 Method Not Allowed, 422 Unprocessable Entity\n\n**Formato de body:** `Content-Type: application/json` en todas las peticiones con cuerpo.",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"variable": [
		{
			"key": "baseUrl",
			"value": "http://localhost/MVC/api/v1",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "token",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string",
			"description": "Bearer token — se guarda automáticamente al ejecutar Login"
		}
	],
	"auth": {
		"type": "bearer",
		"bearer": [
			{
				"key": "token",
				"value": "{{token}}",
				"type": "string"
			}
		]
	},
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "Auth",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Login",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"var json = pm.response.json();",
									"if (json.access_token) {",
									"  pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.access_token);",
									"  console.log('Token guardado:', json.access_token);",
									"}"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"auth": { "type": "noauth" },
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@admin.com\",\n  \"password\": \"admin123\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login",
							"host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
							"path": ["auth", "login"]
						},
						"description": "Autentica al usuario y devuelve un Bearer token. El script 'Tests' guarda el token en la variable de colección `token` automáticamente."
					},
					"response": [
						{
							"name": "200 OK",
							"originalRequest": {
								"method": "POST",
								"body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@admin.com\",\n  \"password\": \"admin123\"\n}" }
							},
							"status": "OK",
							"code": 200,
							"_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
							"body": "{\n  \"access_token\": \"07cbc7e578f625e99fd39f5a6ee2c30c2f00cfa04cb1bfb777d95bac1c87b2d0\",\n  \"token_type\": \"Bearer\",\n  \"user\": {\n    \"id\": 4,\n    \"nombre\": \"Admin\",\n    \"email\": \"admin@admin.com\",\n    \"rol\": \"admin\"\n  }\n}"
						},
						{
